HEADWORD: Tendril
<hw>Ten"dril</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Clasping; climbing as
a tendril.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>Dyer.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

